    </span>
    <span class="tech-row">
      <div class="ruby tech text-center">Ruby</div>
      <div class="slide" id="rubySlide">50%</div>
    </span>
    <span class="tech-row">
      <div class="ruby_on_rails tech text-center">Ruby on Rails</div>
      <div class="slide" id="rubyonrailsSlide">90%</div>
    </span>
    <span class="tech-row">
      <div class="sass tech text-center">Sass</div>
      <div class="slide" id="sassSlide">50%</div>
